VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'to see from a 4K image capture. Now, what I think would be really helpful is to compare both of these generations against what you would expect from taking it from 1080p into 4K using a tool like Topaz Precision 2.5. If you\'re'

[03:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'not already familiar, if you want to up-res your clips utilizing Topaz, which in my opinion is one of the better AI video up-res\'ers on the market, all you have to do is take your lower-res footage, which again is our clean 1080p'

[03:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'version of the video here, and just drag and drop it into the online platform that you can find at astra.app. Okay. So, from here we have the ability to select Starlight precise 2.5. The output'

